<C>__{sister}
<D>__{if you are not listed, i cannot help you sir.}
<C>__{sister }
<D>__{we have strict regulations concerning visitations, which are exclusively for family members.}
<C>__{ben}
<D>__{please, tell her that i came all the way from new york and that i work with dr. kane at st. john's hospital...}
